title: TikTok Plastic Surgeon Comes for Hailey Bieber
description:
Hailey Bieber is many things: a successful model, daughter of a Flintstone and wife to one of pop’s biggest stars, Justin Bieber. But is she a liar? After multiple people and media outlets claim she’s had work done, she sets the record straight and denies it all. Daniel Barrett, a TikTok famous plastic surgeon, begs to differ however. Tune in to hear ALL the deets!
